<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#22863A;--shiki-dark:#85E89D;">    status</span><span style="--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8;">: </span><span style="--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF;">&quot;The actual status message for group1&quot;</span></span>
